room_title: Escape room "The Box" by Amazing Escapes of Boise in Boise
room_address: 6555 W. Overland Rd., Suite 120, Boise, ID 83709
room_description: A secret government program, code-named "Algernon Assay", has been successful with a groundbreaking drug that increases cognitive brain function in 72% of its test subjects. The final phase is to test it on random humans with average intelligence. Unfortunately, the drug is only effective for 56 minutes. Just enough time to escape... the box!
